DataElement.preferredName: CoPaQ Non Prescribed Medication or Dietary Supplement Out of Pocket Payment Number
DataElement.preferredDefinition: Number that represents the patient's out-of-pocket cost for non-prescribed medication or dietary supplements.

DataElementConcept.preferredName: Cost for Patients Questionnaire Not Prescribed Medication Dietary Supplement Out of Pocket Payment
DataElementConcept.preferredDefinition: A questionnaire designed to assess an individual's expenses as a result of their state of health.
